description.en: A thriving Metaverse Resource DAO that allows instant exposure to the top-performing NFTs, play-to-earn models, and player-owned economies. MetaBrands connects people with innovative brands that bridges the relationship between platforms, ecosystems, and games through shared yield for players and DeFi participants in a seamless fashion.
